column5: Was watching an Angling Edge episode, saw this resort featured. I did a search for Lake Kashabowie, didn't see much, especially recent info. This is the Kashabowie near Thunder Bay. Would be interested in hearing of anyone's experience there. Thanks!
we are going to Kashabowie River Resort on upper Shebandowan lake last week of June so I would also be interested any current information.
Here is the name of a resort where I have stayed. The owners are great people. Give them a call.http://birchpointresort.ca/ Regards, Snowball
Anyone out there that can give me any information would be appreciated.
